name: Hook for iPhone - Live DJ and Mashup Workstation

editorialNotes.standard: Just try to stop yourself from nodding along as you make beats. Hook packs enough features to please even pros with its advanced interface, while live DJing gets a special boost from its Flux Fader. Its smooth transitions ensure that the beat drops exactly when we want it to.
